ctrl c / v / x zith no selection						copy / paste / cut line
ctrl shift k											delete line
ctrl enter / shift enter								insert line below / above
alt up / down											move line up / down
ctrl c up / down										copy line above / below
ctrl z / y												undo / redo
ctrl u													undo last cursor operation
ctrl l													select current line
home / end												go to begining / end of line
ctrl home / end											go to beginning / end of file
ctrl up / down											scroll line up / down
ctrl f													find
ctrl h													replace
ctrl k ctrl u											remove line comment
ctrl g [5] enter										go to line 5
ctrl p [myfile]											go to myfile
ctrl shift p [something]								find something
ctrl k, then m											change code language of the file
shift alt up / down										expand cursor up / down
ctrl /													comment / uncomment
ctrl k ctrl o											open a directory
ctrl alt h												add header (extension42 Header)
ctrl shift e											go to files menu

https://code.visualstudio.com/docs/getstarted/keybindings

valgrind --leak-check=full --show-leak-kinds=all ./a.out
